    Captain Irma calls you, gives a salute out of habit, and says, “The team is picking up local radio chatter. Some asteroid miners are having issues drilling with outdated equipment. We could lend them out firepower to punch through the bedrock. Or…” she shrugs, “Could capitalize on the situation to pick up some new recruits. People are always looking for a chance to jump ship, as it were. Otherwise, could be a good chance to dock, get some repairs done.” 
    
